    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重要提示：本试玩版作为《ENTWINE》的免费序章，故事发生在主线剧情之前，不包含完整版游戏的任何直接内容。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >踏入《ENTWINE》令人毛骨悚然又扣人心弦的序章：扮演独立调查记者伊森·米勒，他在调查安德森庄园后神秘失踪。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 破解多重谜题，穿梭于安德森庄园的层层迷宫。在被傀儡本人追杀前，逐步揭开伊森·米勒身后的恐怖真相。      </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >45分钟至1小时游玩时长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >震撼视觉效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >基于Steam Audio技术的双耳立体声技术呈现高保真音效。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以全新视角打造沉重压抑的心理恐怖体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纯粹的孤立感——无干扰NPC或花哨机制，唯有你与它。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >高度聚焦叙事性。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挑战性极强的复杂谜题——灵感源自《寂静岭》等经典作品</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166800/extras/de10ced06213330cd4630afb05df8eb0.poster.avif?t=1771909103\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166800/extras/de10ced06213330cd4630afb05df8eb0.webm?t=1771909103\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166800/extras/de10ced06213330cd4630afb05df8eb0.mp4?t=1771909103\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
